\ip Pol ramav…ôn mam…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo ia kwopun me. Nav…ônien s…ôv…ônhi s…ôro kahar ir…ô r…®no sampam n…ôn…ô in r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe Rom ia nuk 56 u…ô 57. Ia nav…ônien s…ôv…ôi Pol in rokeikei m…ô trukupw…ôn mev…ôn fwe Jerusalem n…ôn…ô mev…ôn mwi fwe taon Rom m…®ne t…ôn…ô Spen. In r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôpn…ôpen…ô t…® nuveheien s…ôv…ônhi. N…ô…°kiariien asori ia n…ôkuku…ô i in i natukwatukwien. Pol ramahat…ôn ia n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô: 1) i…ôrmama riti riw…ôn ratukwatukw; 2) Iesu Kristo …ôpa in ratukwatukw, m…ômher; 3) tr…®ni m…®nu…ô s…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Iesu Kristo, in truvehi raka k…®taha ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi n…ôr…ôhaien, n…ôn…ô muvei pehe n…®m…®ruien vi m k…®taha, n…ôn…ô mo k…®taha satukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn; 4) k…®taha nakalasia me tsam…ôkeikei mhar…ô ia nar…ôien s…ô ro ikinan s…ô Kumwes…ôn rokeikei.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rakupw…ôn  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Wok Me 9:15, 13:2, Kal 1:15\x*Iou Pol. Iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamo tukwini nari m Iesu Kristo. Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôkwein iou m…ô aposol, n…ôn…ô m…ômri karen iou m…ô iou i…ôrmama tak…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 16:25-26\x*N…ô…°kiariien amasan i, in ruv…ôni raka tui ia n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ôi profet me s…ôv…ônhi s…ôm…ôme kamhar…ô ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan.  
\v 3-4 \x - \xo 1:3-4 \xt Mat 22:42, Wok Me 13:33, Rom 9:5, 2Tim 2:8\x*N…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha ram…ô…°kiari ia T…®ni, in n…ôha Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha. In r…®m…ôuvehe i…ôrmama riti r…®m…ôuku pen ia kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Ki…° Tev…®t. In r…®mamh…ô n…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn rahat…ôn m…ô in T…®ni atukwatukw n…ôp…®n ro in r…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Wok Me 26:16-18, Rom 15:18, Kal 2:7-9\x*Ia Kristo, Kumwes…ôn ro ramasan m k…®maha, muvehi pehe wok amasan m k…®maha m…ô k…®maha aposol me. R…®m…ôuvei pehe wok i m k…®maha m…ô tah…ôkwein ia n…ôrmama ia t…ôn…ômt…ôn…ô me pam m…ô tuh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô, mho n…ôkwan. N…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n ir…ôha kamho iam…®nha ir…ô, mamh…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ô…°hi Iesu.   
\p
\v 6 Wok i r…®neste k…®miaha mwi. K…®miaha n…ôrmama Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôkwein ia k…®miaha m…ô k…®miaha s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Nam 6:25-26, 1Kor 1:2, 2Kor 1:1, Efes 1:2\x*N…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha pam fwe taon n…ôha Rom. Kumwes…ôn rokeikei k…®miaha, m…ôkwein k…®miaha m…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi. Pw…ôh Kumwes…ôn tata s…ôk…®taha, m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha trou…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha.   
\s1 Pol rokeikei m…ô trev…ôn m…ôtoni n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo ia taon n…ôha Rom  
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt 1Tes 1:8\x*Kurir…ô iak…ô…°kiari iaku…ô ia n…ô…°hi Iesu Kristo tak…®ni vivi Kumwes…ôn s…ôiou tukumiaha pam t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama ia t…ôn…ômt…ôn…ô me pam kamh…ôre…°i n…ôvisauien ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Efes 1:16, Fil 1:8, 1Tes 2:5,10\x*Kumwes…ôn s…ô iakamo tukwini nari min ia rer…®k pam t…® n…®ni irapwien n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi T…®ni, in r…®n…ôt…ô raka noien s…ôiou mukur…ôn m…ô ia n…ôp…®n me pam iakani k…®miaha  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Wok Me 19:21, Rom 15:23,32\x*ia n…ôfwakiien me s…ôiou. Iakam…ôres m…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien p…ôrhien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, in tr…ôsev…ôr ia suatuk riti pw…ôh iakuvehe m…ôtoni k…®miaha r…ômwhen iak…®neitenhi tui m…ô tako.   
\p
\v 11 Iakokeikei p…®k m…ô takuvehe m…ôtoni k…®miaha muvehi pehe nasituien riti s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan pw…ôh r…ôrpwi …ôknek…®n mwi k…®miaha.  
\v 12 N…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien i m…ô nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha rukur…ôn nasituien ia nirak n…ôn…ô s…ôiou mwi rukur…ôn nasituien ia k…®miaha.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Wok Me 19:21, Jon 15:16\x*Piak me ramasan m…ô tih…ôukur…ôn m…ô n…ôp…®n r…®p…®k rer…®k ramrhi m…ô takuvehe m…ôti pehe ia k…®miaha, m…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n me pam narimnari me r…®p…®k ram…ôsis…ô…° iou t…® nuveheien. Iakokeikei m…ô wok s…ôiou truku…ô mo kw…ônkwan ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha r…ômwhen ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel ia kwopun me.   
\p
\v 14 Iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô takam…ôkeikei m…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn m n…ôrmama me pam, n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ôukur…ôn n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Kris m…®ne noien s…ôv…ônraha, m…®ne n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme ir…ôha h…ôreirei, m…®ne s…ôm…ôme ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn amasan nari, m…®ne s…ôm…ôme h…ôpw…ôh nukur…ôn amasanien nari.  
\v 15 Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô iakokeikei p…®k m…ô tak…ôvisau irapw mwi n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn m k…®miaha fwe taon n…ôha Rom.   
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Sam 119:46, Mak 8:38, 1Kor 1:18-24, Wok Me 13:46\x*Iakam…ô…°kiari iam…®nhi ir…ô iou iapkaur…®s anan mh…ô t…® n…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha in n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn t…® nuvehim…®ruien n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô, r…®m…ôkupw…ôn muvehe t…® n…ôkur Isrel, kurir…ô rev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Rom 3:21-22, Hab 2:4\x*Ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi, Kumwes…ôn ramo n…ôrmama kamh…ôtoni suatuk s…ô in r…®n…ômri ir…ôha tuhesi pen tro ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen. Suatuk n…ôha in nahat…ôt…ôien fwe nukunen mamev…ôn meste n…ôkr…ôkwer…®n sampam.\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Suatuk riti mwi t…® n…®niien n…ô…°kiariien i ia vas 17 in i m…ô, ‚ÄúIa n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi Kumwes…ôn ramo n…ôrmama kamh…ôtoni natukwatukwien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô raku pen t…® nahat…ôt…ôien mamev…ôn ia nahat…ôt…ôien.‚Äù\f* R…ômwhen ia n…ô…°kiariien i k…®m…ôrai pen ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúI…ôrmama s…ô ratukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônhi,  
\q2 in truvehi n…®m…®ruien.‚Äù   
\s1 Kumwes…ôn niemaha ram…ôpi t…® noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama  
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Efes 5:6, Kol 3:6, 2Tes 2:12\x*Kumwes…ôn fwe ia neiai ramo n…ôrmama kamh…ôtoni m…ô niemaha ram…ôpi p…®k in. In ram…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me pam s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrui n…ôkwan mamh…ôrer tukuaha…° ia n…®p…ôrhienien s…ôv…ônhi ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Wok Me 14:15-17, Wok Me 17:24-28\x*In ram…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn n…ôtoni atukwatukwien narimnari me pam s…ôm…ôme n…ôrmama h…ôukur…ôn n…ôtoniien Kumwes…ôn ir…ô. Kamho iam…®nha ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn atukw r…®nahat…ôn atukwatukw ir…ôha ir…ô.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Job 12:7-9, Sam 19:1, Hip 11:3\x*Fwe nukune nar…ôien muvehe meste pehe ipwet m…®ne n…ôrmama me pam h…ôukur…ôn n…ôtoniien ia n…ônimenraha narimnari me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn r…®no ia neiai m…®ne t…®pr…ôn…ô, n…ôn…ô ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô ir…ôha ko h…ôpk…ôtoni mh…ô Kumwes…ôn ia n…ônimenraha, m…ôt…ô h…ôukur…ôn n…ôtoniien ia narimnari me n…ôha m…ô n…®skaiien s…ôv…ônhi ramev…ôn a m…®pko mh…ô sampam m…®ne n…®p…ôrhienien m…ô in Kumwes…ôn. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ô…°kiariien riti riw…ôn ko ir…ôha h…ôni.   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Efes 4:17-18\x*Ir…ôha h…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka Kumwes…ôn, m…ôt…ô h…ôpw…ôh nuvehi ut…ôien n…ô…°h…®n m…ô in Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô mh…ôpw…ôh n…®niien tanak tukwe in. M…ôt…ô rer…®nraha ruvehe m…®pkrhi amasan mh…ô nari, n…ôn…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha ruvehe m…®reirei nari r…ômwhen m…ô kamhar…ô ia n…ôpit…ôvien.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Jer 10:14, 1Kor 1:20\x*Ir…ôha kamh…ôni m…ô h…ôukur…ôn nari, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha h…ôreirei nari,  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Dut 4:15-19, Sam 106:20\x*mh…ôn…ôpw…ôh n…ôfwakiien m Kumwes…ôn asori s…ô tr…®pkemh…ô mh…ô ia n…ôp…®n riti, n…ôn…ô mh…ôuv…ôn mh…ôfwaki pen m n…ôn…®mwi nari me s…ôm…ôme h…ômwhen ia i…ôrmama s…ô tremh…ô, u…ô menu me, u…ô n…ôrim…®ru me s…ôm…ôme kamhav…ôn u…ô kamh…ôrkou.   
\p
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Wok Me 14:16\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô Kumwes…ôn r…ôpw…ôh ir…ôha, m…ôseni ir…ôha m…ô ir…ôha tuhamesi pen a noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôm…ôme rer…®nraha rokeikei p…®k m…ô tuho. Ro pen ir…ôha kamho ia nir…ôha me noien me ia n…®pwranraha s…ô ro a naur…®sien.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Jer 13:25, Jer 16:19, Rom 9:5\x*Ir…ôha h…ôn…ôpw…ôh n…®p…ôrhienien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, mh…ôkwt…ômhiri neiku…ôien, n…ôn…ô mamh…ôfwaki pen m narimnari me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn r…®no ia neiai m…®ne t…®pr…ôn…ô, mamho tukwini nari m…®nraha, m…ôt…ô h…ôpw…ôh n…ôfwakiien m Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®no neiai m…®ne t…®pr…ôn…ô, mh…ôpw…ôh no tukwiniien nari min. In n…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ô kam…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni rer…®n in. Ou…ôh, pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   
\p
\v 26 T…® noien n…ôha ir…ôha kamho, Kumwes…ôn r…ôpw…ôh ir…ôha, m…ôseni ir…ôha m…ô ir…ôha tuhamesi pen a noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôm…ôme rer…®nraha rokeikei p…®k m…ô tuho s…ô ro a naur…®sien. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…®pran me nepw…®n s…ôv…ônraha kamh…ôpw…ôh noien i ratukwatukw, noien s…ô pran ramesi pen i…ôrman s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô mh…ôuv…ôn mamho noien i r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô, noien s…ô pran ramiri pran.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Lev 18:22, Lev 20:13, 1Kor 6:9\x*Ia noien a mwi n…ôha, n…ôrman me nepw…®n s…ôv…ônraha kamh…ôpw…ôh noien i ratukwatukw, noien s…ô i…ôrman ramiri pran s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô mh…ôuv…ôn rer…®nraha ramev…ôn p…®k ia nir…ôha me. N…ôrman kamho noien me nepw…®n ia nir…ôha me s…ô ro a naur…®sien. M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôuvei pen raka n…ôrpw…®nien m…®nraha resi pen atukwatukw noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha.   
\p
\v 28 T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama h…ôpkokeikei mh…ô m…ô tuh…ôukur…ôn Kumwes…ôn, in r…ôpw…ôh ir…ôha, m…ôseni ir…ôha m…ô ir…ôha tuhamesi pen a n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien ikou me s…ôv…ônraha, mamho noien me h…ôpw…ôh n…ômwhenien.  
\v 29 Rer…®nraha ruku…ôr ia noien …ôr…ôha m…®ne noien ourour me pam. Ir…ôha kamh…ôpwt…®…° t…® naut…ô s…ôv…ônraha, mamh…ômw…ôki n…ôrmama. Rer…®nraha ruku…ôr ia nakresien, nousi …ôpuneien i…ôrmama, n…ôvis…ôien, neiku…ôien, m…®ne n…ôtuiien suatuk t…® nourahaien i…ôrmama. Ir…ôha kamh…ôni n…®kare n…ôrmama,  
\v 30 mamhouraha n…ô…°hi n…ôrmama ia neiku…ôien me. Ir…ôha kamh…ômw…ôki Kumwes…ôn. Ir…ôha kamh…ôkwa…° raka ia n…ô…°kiariien, mamh…ôfi…ôut…ô ia nir…ôha, mamh…ôrpwi ir…ôha ia n…ôp…®n me. Ir…ôha kamh…ôtui suatuk t…® noien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôm…ôme n…ôrmama h…ôpw…ôh ihi nukur…ônien. Ir…ôha kamh…ôrui n…ôkwai tata m…®ne mama.  
\v 31 Ia rer…®nraha ir…ôha h…ôreirei nari. Ir…ôha kamh…ôtefi n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ônraha. Nokeikeiien s…ôv…ônraha riw…ôn t…® i…ôrmama. Ir…ôha h…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien nas…ôkien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama t…® nasituien ia nir…ôha.  
\v 32 Ir…ôha h…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka m…ô n…ô…°kiariien atukwatukw s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn rani m…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho noien me i iam…®nha ir…ô tuham…ôkeikei mhemh…ô, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha kamh…ômwur pen ia noien me n…ôha. R…®pko mh…ô noien …ôpa n…ôha ir…ôha kamho, m…ôt…ô kamh…ôseni mwi n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme kamho noien me n…ôha m…ô ramasan a.   
\c 2  
\s1 Kumwes…ôn ram…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama ia noien atukwatukw  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mat 7:1-2, Jon 8:7\x*Ro pen n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô ik n…ôfe i…ôrmama, ikamo noien riti r…ôpw…ôh n…ômwhenien n…ôp…®n ikam…ôkiri noien s…ôv…ôi i…ôrm…ôp…ô. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô ik…®ni pen t…® i…ôrmama riti m…ô s…ôv…ônhi noien r…ôr…ôha, m…ôt…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ikani ikamousi atukw a ik. Ik n…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ikam…ôkiri noien s…ôv…ônhi, m…ôt…ô ik mwi ikamo noien …ôr…ôha r…ômwhen ir…ô.  
\v 2 K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn m…ô Kumwes…ôn ramo noien s…ô ratukwatukw a n…ôp…®n ram…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ô ro me iam…®nha ir…ô.  
\v 3 Ik s…ô ikam…ôkiri noien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrm…ôp…ô, n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôim r…ôfo? M…ô ik mwi ikamo noien …ôr…ôha me n…ôha ir…ôha kamho, n…ôp…®n Kumwes…ôn tr…ôkiri noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôim ko ikap raka ir…ô? Rek…ôm!  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Efes 1:7, 2:9, 2Tes 3:15\x*U…ô rosi ikam…ôt…ô …ôr…ôha noien i s…ô Kumwes…ôn ramo ia niram u…ô? In ramo ramasan p…®k tukw ik, n…ôn…ô m…ôpw…ôh n…ômw…ôki akwauakwien ik, n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi r…ôpw…ômw…®s tukw ik. Ikukur…ôn u…ô rek…ôm m…ô ramo noien amasan me mik m…ô noien n…ôha triri pen ik ikev…ôn m…ôpw…ôh noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôim m…®r…ôr…®…° ia rer…®m?   
\p
\v 5 M…ôt…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…ômkapw…ô r…®skai, ik…ôpw…ôh narakaien ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôim m…®r…ôr…®…° ia rer…®m. N…ôn…ô ro iam…®nhi ir…ô ikamoeite niemaha s…ô tukuvei pehe mik ia n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi niemaha. Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Kumwes…ôn tro n…ôrmama h…ôtoni n…ôkiriien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ratukwatukw,  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Mat 16:27, Jon 5:29, 2Kor 5:10\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in tr…ôr…ôku n…ôrmama kuatia kuatia resi pen n…ôfe noien me h…ôno.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 2Tes 1:8\x*N…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrer …ôknek…®n t…® noien noien amasan ia n…ôp…®n me m…ô tuh…ôuvehi n…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien, m…®ne n…®siaiien, m…®ne n…®m…®ruien i nemh…ôien riw…ôn ir…ô, Kumwes…ôn truvei pen n…®m…®ruien rer…®n m…®nraha.  
\v 8 M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme kamho a nari rer…®nraha rokeikei, n…ôn…ô, mamh…ôuvei pen t…ôkutanraha m n…®p…ôrhienien, mamhesi pen a noien …ôr…ôha me, Kumwes…ôn truvei pen niemaha asori s…ôv…ônhi m…®nraha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Rom 1:16\x*N…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamho noien …ôr…ôha, Kumwes…ôn tro n…ômis…ôien m…®nraha, mo n…ôknek…®nien m…®nraha, trukupw…ôn ia n…ôkur Isrel kurir…ô n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 10 M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamho noien amasan, Kumwes…ôn truvei pen n…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien, m…®ne n…®siaien, m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m…®nraha, trukupw…ôn ia n…ôkur Isrel, kurir…ô n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Efes 6:9, 1Pit 1:17\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn tro r…ômn…ômwhen pam ia n…ôrmama me pam.   
\p
\v 12 In tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel n…ôri au…ôr a h…ôpkuvehi mh…ô Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses. N…ôn…ô n…ôkur Isrel me kamh…ôuvehi Loa n…ôha, Kumwes…ôn tr…ôkiri noien me s…ôv…ônraha ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Loa n…ôha, n…ôn…ô m…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha ir…ô.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Mat 7:21, 1Jon 3:7\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô r…®pko mh…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôre…°i Loa n…ôha ir…ôha n…ô hatukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, m…ôt…ô n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme kamho n…ôri Loa n…ôha rani, ir…ôha n…ôha Kumwes…ôn tr…®ni irapw m…ô ir…ôha hatukwatukw.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Wok Me 10:35\x*N…®p…ôrhienien n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel ir…ôha h…ôpw…ôh nuvehiien Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, m…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n me nepw…®n ir…ôha kamhesi pen a n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha, mamho n…ôri s…ô ratukwatukw r…ômwhen a ia Loa n…ôha rani. Ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia loa riti ramiri atukw a ir…ôha, n…ôri au…ôr a ir…ôha h…ôpkuvehi mh…ô Loa n…ôha.  
\v 15 Noien s…ôv…ônraha ramahat…ôn pen m…ô n…®pwrai Loa n…ôha ik…®n k…®m…ôrai pen ram…ômak ia rer…®nraha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n nepw…®n ir…ôha h…ôre…°i pen fwe ia rer…®nraha m…ô h…ôno noien …ôr…ôha, n…ôp…®n nepw…®n mwi m…ô h…ôno noien amasan.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt 2Tim 2:8\x*Ir…ôha tuh…ôre…°i pen n…ôri me i iam…®nha ir…ô fwe ia rer…®nraha ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Kumwes…ôn tr…ôseni Iesu Kristo ir…ô m…ô tr…ôkiri n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama, n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrkwaf…ô. N…ô…°kiariien i ramesi pen n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô iakam…ôvisau irapw i.   
\s1 N…ôkur Isrel m…®ne Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses  
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Jem 2:19\x*M…ôt…ô m…ô ik i…ôrmama riti n…ô ikani m…ô ik i…ôm…ô Isrel r…ôfo ia niram? Ik ik…ôt…®…°ite ia Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, mam…ôfi…ôut…ô ik m…ô ik ikukur…ôn Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô in rukur…ôn ik.  
\v 18 Ik ikani m…ô ikuv…ôukur…ôn raka n…ôfe Kumwes…ôn rokeikei m…ô tiko, n…ôn…ô, mukur…ôn suatuk s…ô ratukwatukw amasan t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Loa n…ôha r…®nahat…ôn ik ir…ô.  
\v 19 Ikani m…ô ik i…ôrmama ikamiri n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme n…ônimenraha r…®fw…ô, n…ôn…ô mam…ôhi…ôpw…®n suatuk s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamhav…ôn ia kwopun r…®pit…ôv ik…®n,  
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt 2Tim 3:5,15, Mat 15:14, Luk 18:9\x*n…ôn…ô mamahat…ôn n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme h…ôreirei nari m…®ne n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me. Ik ikani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ikauvehi Loa s…ô nukur…ônien m…®ne n…®p…ôrhienien me pam kamhar…ô ir…ô.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Sam 50:16-21, Mat 23:3-4\x*Ik ikamahat…ôn n…ôrmama …ôp…ô me, m…ôt…ô r…ôfo ipkahat…ôn atukw a mh…ô ik? Ikamahat…ôn n…ôrmama me m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôpw…ôh nakresien, m…ôt…ô ikamakres u…ô rek…ôm?  
\v 22 Ikamahat…ôn n…ôrmama me m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôpw…ôh nakresien pran s…ôv…ôi i…ôrm…ôp…ô, m…ôt…ô ikamakres pran s…ôv…ôi i…ôrm…ôp…ô u…ô rek…ôm? Ikam…ômw…ôki n…ôn…®mwi nari me s…ôm…ôme kam…ôfwaki pen m…®nraha, m…ôt…ô ikamakres ia narimnari me ia nimw…ôfwaki me s…ôv…ôi n…ôn…®mwi nari me n…ôha u…ô rek…ôm?  
