\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Aes 52:5, Esik 36:20\x*Ou…ôh, ikamo noien …ôr…ôha me pam n…ôha. Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ô…°kiariien i k…®m…ôrai pen ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel kamh…ôni …ôr…ôha n…ô…°hi Kumwes…ôn t…® noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®miaha.‚Äù   
\p
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Jer 4:4, 9:25\x*Ik i…ôm…ô Isrel, tr…®ni m…®nu…ô ikamesi pen Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, noien n…ôha k…®no ia niram kuvehi ninhum mik t…® Loa n…ôha rukur…ôn nasituien ia niram. M…ôt…ô m…ô ikam…ôrui Loa n…ôha, n…ôn…ô r…ômwhen a m…ô k…ôpw…ôh nuvehiien ninhum mik.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 2:26 \xt Kal 5:6\x*Ia noien a mwi n…ôha, i…ôrmama riti r…®pko mh…ô in i…ôm…ô Isrel, k…ôpw…ôh nuvehiien ninhum min, m…ôt…ô ramesi pen narimnari me s…ôm…ôme Loa n…ôha rani, Kumwes…ôn tr…ôtoni m…ô kuv…ôuvehi raka ninhum min, n…ôn…ô in i…ôrmama s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 27 I…ôrmama s…ô r…®pko mh…ô in i…ôm…ô Isrel, k…ôpw…ôh nuvehiien ninhum min, m…ôt…ô ramesi pen Loa n…ôha, in tr…ôkiri ik m…ô noien s…ôim r…ôr…ôha. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô ik ikauvehi Loa s…ô k…®m…ôrai, n…ôn…ô kuvehi ninhum mik, m…ôt…ô ikam…ôrui Loa n…ôha.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 2:28 \xt Jon 7:24, 8:39\x*I…ôrmama i in i…ôm…ô Isrel ia n…®pwran iru…ô r…®pko mh…ô in i…ôm…ô Isrel p…ôrhien, n…ôn…ô, noien p…ôrhien s…ôv…ôi nuvehiien ninhum m i…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô in nari riti s…ô kamo ia n…®pwrai i…ôrmama iru…ô.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 2:29 \xt Dut 30:6, Kol 2:11, 1Kor 4:5, 2Kor 10:18\x*M…ôt…ô i…ôrmama i in i…ôm…ô Isrel p…ôrhien ia rer…®n in i…ôm…ô Isrel. N…ôn…ô noien p…ôrhien s…ôv…ôi nuvehiien ninhum m i…ôrmama, in nari riti ram…ômak ia reri i…ôrmama N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan ramo, m…ôt…ô r…®pko mh…ô Loa ramo. N…ôn…ô r…®pko mh…ô n…ôrmama kamh…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni i…ôrmama n…ôha, m…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn …ôpa ram…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in.   
\c 3  
\s1 Kumwes…ôn ramo noien atukwatukw ia n…ôp…®n me  
\p
\v 1 M…ô ro iam…®nhi ir…ô, r…ôfo noien n…ôha ramasan m…ô i…ôrmama riti in i…ôm…ô Isrel? U…ô r…ôfo noien n…ôha ramasan m…ô kuvehi ninhum min?  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Sam 147:19-20, Rom 9:4\x*Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama riti in i…ôm…ô Isrel ramasan p…®k anan. N…ôri s…ô ramasan mukupw…ôn, n…ôkur Isrel ir…ôha n…ô n…ôrmama Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ômri pen n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi ia r…ô…°…®nraha m…ô tuh…ôtui amasan tukwe.   
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Rom 9:6, 11:29, 2Tim 2:13\x*N…®p…ôrhienien ir…ôha me nepw…®n h…ôpw…ôh n…®niien n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha, m…ôt…ô noien n…ôha ir…ôha h…ôno, mh…ôpw…ôh n…®niien n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi, ko r…®pk…®nise mh…ô ia Kumwes…ôn m…ô tr…ôpw…ôh noien n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 4 Rek…ôm! N…ôri au…ôr a n…ôrmama me pam ia t…®pr…ôn…ô kamheiku…ô, m…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®pkeiku…ô mh…ô. R…ômwhen ia n…ô…°kiariien i k…®m…ôrai pen ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan ram…ô…°kiari ia Kumwes…ôn mani m…®nu…ô:  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…ôp…®n ikam…ô…°kiari, n…ô…°kiariien s…ôim trahat…ôn m…ô ik ikatukwatukw.  
\q2 N…ôp…®n n…ôrmama tuh…ôkiri noien me s…ôim, mh…ôni m…ô ik…®no noien …ôr…ôha me, m…ôt…ô ik tik…ôsis…ô…° ia t…ôrhunraha.‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 M…ôt…ô m…ô noien …ôr…ôha s…ôk…®taha ramahat…ôn pen m…ô Kumwes…ôn ramo noien atukwatukw ia n…ôp…®n me n…ôn…ô k…®taha ts…ôfni ir…ô? R…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô Kumwes…ôn ruvei pehe niemaha m k…®taha? Iakam…ôres iam…®nha ir…ô mamesi pen n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama nepw…®n.  
\v 6 M…ôt…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien n…ôha r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien n…ôha ro n…®p…ôrhienien, n…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôf…ôkiri n…ôrmama ia t…®pr…ôn…ô t…® noien me s…ôv…ônraha?  
\v 7 M…ôt…ô r…ôfo i…ôrmama riti r…®ni m…ô, ‚ÄúTr…®ni m…®nu…ô iakeiku…ô, n…ôn…ô neiku…ôien s…ôiou rahat…ôn pen m…ô Kumwes…ôn rani a n…®p…ôrhienien, n…ôn…ô n…ôrmama kamh…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ô…°h…®n tukwe, r…ôfo Kumwes…ôn ram…ôkiri ihi m…ô iou s…ôiou noien r…ôr…ôha?‚Äù  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Rom 6:1,15\x*N…ôn…ô r…ôfo i…ôrmama riti r…®ni m…ô, ‚ÄúRamasan m…ô k…®taha tsamo a noien …ôr…ôha pw…ôh ruku…ô ia namasanien.‚Äù N…®p…ôrhienien, n…ôrmama nepw…®n kamh…ôni …ôr…ôha n…ô…°h…®maha, mamheiku…ô m…ô k…®maha iaham…ô…°kiari iam…®nha ir…ô. Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônraha, n…ôn…ô, ratukwatukw a m…ô in tro.   
\s1 I…ôrmama riti riw…ôn ratukwatukw  
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Rom 1:18-2:24, Rom 3:23\x*Ro pen, r…ôfo? K…®maha n…ôkur Isrel iahatukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn mh…ôpi raka n…ôrmama nepw…®n? Rek…ôm! Iakuv…ôni raka m…ô n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi noien …ôr…ôha ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia n…ôrmama me pam, n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel.  
