\v 14 ‚ÄúN…®p…ô…°i n…ôkwanraha ruku…ôr ia n…ôkunanien i…ôrmama m…®ne n…ô…°kiariien …ôfi…ô.‚Äù   
\q1
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Prov 1:16\x*‚ÄúN…®sunraha me kamhaiu akwauakw t…® nousi …ôpuneien i…ôrmama.   
\q2
\v 16 Ia kwopun me pam kamh…ôuv…ôn ik…®n, ir…ôha kamhouraha narimnari, mamho n…ôrmama kamh…ôre…°i r…ôr…ôha.   
\q1
\v 17 Ir…ôha h…ôreirei anan suatuk s…ôv…ôi n…ôm…ôrinuien.‚Äù   
\q2
\v 18 ‚ÄúIr…ôha h…ôpw…ôh nehek…®rien Kumwes…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 19 K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn m…ô narimnari me pam s…ôm…ôme Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses rani narimnari me n…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen Loa n…ôha m…®nraha. Loa n…ôha ram…ô…°kiari m…®nraha, mam…ôsis…ô…° ia t…ôrhunraha pam, mamo n…ôrmama pam ia t…ôkure t…®pr…ôn…ô h…ôtoni m…ô noien s…ôv…ônraha r…ôr…ôha ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Sam 143:2, Rom 7:7, Kal 2:16\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô i…ôrmama riti s…ô tratukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn ia nesi penien Loa riw…ôn, m…ôt…ô ia Loa k…®taha pam s…ôukur…ôn m…ô k…®taha samo noien …ôr…ôha.   
\s1 N…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn  
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Wok Me 10:43\x*M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni Kumwes…ôn r…®no raka n…ôrmama kamh…ôtoni suatuk s…ô in r…®n…ômri tuhesi pen tro ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen. Suatuk n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô in i tuhesi pen Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses. M…ôt…ô n…ô…°kiariien me ia Loa n…ôha m…®ne n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ôi profet me fwe kupw…ôn kamh…ô…°kiari ia suatuk n…ôha m…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Rom 1:17, Kal 2:16\x*Suatuk n…ôha in i n…ôrmama tuhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo. N…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô Kumwes…ôn ramo ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen. N…ôri au…ôr a m…ô ir…ôha n…ôfe n…ôrmama t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha pam h…ômn…ômwhen a.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Rom 3:9, 5:2\x*N…ôrmama me pam h…ôno noien …ôr…ôha n…ôn…ô mharfai ia suatuk atukwatukw s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ô ramasan mamser,  
\v 24 \x - \xo 3:24 \xt Rom 5:1, Efes 2:8\x*m…ôt…ô ia namasanien s…ôv…ônhi Kumwes…ôn ramasitu ia nir…ôha, mamo ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Iesu Kristo r…®n…ôr…ôku suatuk s…ôv…ônraha, meivi nari ia nir…ôha ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Efes 1:7\x*Kumwes…ôn r…ôrhi pehe Kristo ruvehe n…®ten raiu t…® nuvehi rakaien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama. N…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn ruvehi raka noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama n…ôp…®n ir…ôha hahat…ôt…ô ia Kristo m…ô in r…®mamh…ô t…® nir…ôha. Kumwes…ôn r…®no suatuk n…ôha m…ô trahat…ôn m…ô noien s…ôv…ônhi ratukwatukw t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi r…ôpw…ômw…®s in r…ôpw…ôh n…ôrpw…®nien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ôno fwe kupw…ôn.  
\v 26 Kumwes…ôn ro iam…®nha ir…ô ipwet m…®ne m…ô trahat…ôn m…ô in ratukwatukw, n…ôn…ô in ram…®ni n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu m…ô ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen.   
\p
\v 27 \x - \xo 3:27 \xt 1Kor 1:31\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôfe mwi n…ôha ik…®n k…®taha s…ôukur…ôn n…ôfi…ôut…ôien k…®taha tukwe? Nari riti mwi riw…ôn! T…® n…ôfe? T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha s…ôpkatukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn ia noien me s…ôk…®taha, m…ôt…ô k…®taha satukwatukw ia n…ônimen ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®taha.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 3:28 \xt Kal 2:16\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha sam…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien i m…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ramahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu in ratukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, m…ôt…ô r…®pko mh…ô ia nesi penien Loa.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 3:29 \xt Rom 10:12\x*U…ô r…ôfo? Kumwes…ôn in Kumwes…ôn s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel …ôpa? Rosi in mwi Kumwes…ôn s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel u…ô? Ou…ôh, in mwi Kumwes…ôn s…ôv…ônraha,  
\v 30 \x - \xo 3:30 \xt Dut 6:4, Rom 4:11-12, Kal 3:20\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn kuatia a. N…ôn…ô in tr…®ni irapw m…ô n…ôrmama me i kamhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen. Noien n…ôha tro r…ômwhen a mwi ia n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 3:31 \xt Mat 5:17, Rom 8:4\x*R…ôfo n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni ia Loa n…ôha? Nahat…ôt…ôien n…ôha ramo Loa n…ôha in n…ôri au…ôr a? Rek…ôm! M…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n samahat…ôt…ô ia Kumwes…ôn, samesi pen atukwatukw suatuk p…ôrhien s…ôv…ôi Loa.   
\c 4  
\s1 Epraham ruvehe matukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônhi  
\p
