\v 16 \x - \xo 15:16 \xt Rom 1:5, 12:3, Rom 11:13, Fil 2:17\x*muvehi ut…ô iou ir…ô m…ô iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo\f + \fr 15:16 \ft U…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ramo tukwini nari m Iesu Kristo\f* k…ôrhi pen iou iakamev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. Iou iakamowok r…ômwhen ia pris riti, mam…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn. R…ômwhen ia pris rauvei pen narimnari me m Kumwes…ôn ia t…ôkure n…®fat…ô, iou mwi iakauvei pen nari riti min. N…ôri n…ôha iakauvei pen m Kumwes…ôn in i n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. N…ôn…ô iakokeikei m…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan tro ir…ôha h…ôuvehe mh…ômher, mho ikinan i, n…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn rer…®n tra…°ien t…® nuvehiien ir…ôha.   
\p
