\v 19 N…ôn…ô in r…®no wok ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi n…®mt…ôtien me m…®ne narimnari me kam…ôtoni kam…ôrk…ôrinari ir…ô. In r…®no ir…ôha pam ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan. Ro pen iak…®ni irapw pam n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo, iak…®m…ôkupw…ôn fwe Jerusalem mev…ôn ia kwopun me pam meste pen t…ôn…ô n…ôha Ilirikam.  
