\v 3 \x - \xo 16:3 \xt Wok Me 18:2,18,26\x*Tih…ôni tukwini ramasan s…ôiou rev…ôn t…® Prisila m…®ne Akwila, k…®mrahar m…®nrau iamharo p…ôri wok s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo.  
