\p Tih…ôni tukwini ramasan s…ôiou rev…ôn t…® i…ôrmama keikei s…ôiou Epainetas, in r…®m…ôkupw…ôn m…®ni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Kristo fwe ia profens n…ôha Esia.   
