\v 12 Tih…ôni tukwini ramasan s…ôiou rev…ôn t…® Trifaena m…®ne Trifosa, pr…ôn mi n…ôha krauo wok s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.  
