\v 15 Tih…ôni tukwini ramasan s…ôiou rev…ôn t…® Filolokas, m…®ne Julia m…®ne Nereas irau k…®tirim…ôni, m…®ne Olimpas, m…®ne n…ôrmama me nepw…®n s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ôm…ôme kamhar…ô ir…ôha m…®nraha.   
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 16:16 \xt 1Kor 16:20, 1Tes 5:14\x*Tih…ôni ramasan tukumiaha me, mhakei m k…®miaha me ia nakeiien s…ô r…ômher. Nakalasia me pam s…ôv…ôi Kristo kamh…ôni ramasan tukumiaha.   
