\v 17 \x - \xo 16:17 \xt Mat 7:15, Taet 3:10\x*Piak me, iakam…ô…°kiari skai m k…®miaha m…ô tiham…ôsiari t…® n…ôrmama nepw…®n n…ôha ik…®n. Ir…ôha kamh…ôrukwumen n…ôvis…ôien me, mamhouraha nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama, mamhahat…ôn n…ô…°kiariien s…ô rop…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien i k…®nahat…ôn raka k…®miaha ir…ô. Tih…ôpw…ôh nev…ônien ipaka t…® nir…ôha,  
\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt Fil 3:19, Kol 2:4, 2Tes 2:3\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho iam…®nha ir…ô, ir…ôha h…ôpko tukwini mh…ô nari m Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha kamho tukwini nari m t…®pw…®nraha. N…ôn…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien …ôsien me m…®ne n…ô…°kiariien me h…ôpw…ôh n…ômwhenien, ir…ôha kamheiku…ô ia n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme h…ôpkukur…ôn amasan mh…ô nari.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 16:19 \xt Rom 1:8, Mat 10:16, 1Kor 14:20\x*N…ôrmama h…ôuv…ôre…°i raka n…ôvisauien m…ô k…®miaha hiamo n…ôkwai Kristo, ro pen rer…®k ra…°ien p…®k tukumiaha. M…ôt…ô iakokeikei p…®k m…ô tih…ôukur…ôn amasan nari t…® noien atukwatukw me, n…ôn…ô mh…ôpw…ôh nev…ônien ia noien …ôr…ôha me.   
\p
\v 20 \x - \xo 16:20 \xt Rom 15:33, Jen 3:15\x*Kumwes…ôn in nukune n…ôm…ôrinuien tr…®pko mh…ô tui in tr…ôseni k…®miaha hieiv…ô tesi Setan ia n…®sumiaha. Pw…ôh namasanien s…ôv…ôi Iesu I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha tramar…ô tukumiaha.   
