\v 22 Iou Tertius i iakm…ôrai tukwini n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Pol ia n…ôkuku…ô i iakani ramasan tukumiaha ia n…ô…°hi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.   
