\v 23 \x - \xo 16:23 \xt 1Kor 1:14\x*I…ôm…ô i Kaius rani ramasan tukumiaha. Iou Pol, iakamar…ô ia nimw…ô s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô nakalasia me kamhous…ôs…®mw…®n ir…ôha me ia nimw…ô s…ôv…ônhi ir…ôha pam kamh…ôni ramasan tukumiaha. Erastas i ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia mane me s…ôv…ôi taon n…ôha m…®ne pi…ôvtaha Kwotas, irau mwi krauni ramasan tukumiaha.  
\v 24 \f + \fr 16:24 \ft Niutestamen me nepw…®n k…®m…ôrai pen ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Kris fwe kupw…ôn n…ô…°kiariien riti ia vas 24 rani iam…®nhi ir…ô m…®nu…ô: ‚ÄúPw…ôh namasanien s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo tramar…ô tukumiaha pam.‚Äù\f*   
\p
\v 25 \x - \xo 16:25 \xt Efes 1:9, 3:5,9, Kol 1:26, Rom 1:5\x*Pw…ôh s…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ô…°hi Kumwes…ôn rev…ôn fwe ir…ônh…ô ia n…ôp…®n me. In …ôpa rukur…ôn noien k…®miaha hi…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha. Noien n…ôha ramesi pen n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôiou m…®ne n…ôvisauien ia Iesu Kristo. Ramesi pen mwi n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ô n…®pwran r…®n…ôrkwaf…ô fwe tui,  
\v 26 m…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni m…®ne Kumwes…ôn r…®no pui n…ôrmama h…ôtoni. In Kumwes…ôn s…ô ramar…ô rer…®n. Profet me s…ôv…ônhi me fwe kupw…ôn h…ôm…ôrai pen n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi ia n…ôkuku…ô me s…ôv…ônraha. In r…®ni m…ô n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha tram…ôkeikei mev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama ia t…ôn…ômt…ôn…ô me pam m…ô ir…ôha tuhahat…ôt…ô ir…ô mho n…ôkwan.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 16:27 \xt 1Tim 1:17, Jut 25\x*Kumwes…ôn …ôpa in Kumwes…ôn, in …ôpa rukur…ôn nari. Pw…ôh n…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien rev…ôn tukwe in ia nuk nuk me t…® n…ôri i Iesu Kristo r…®no. Ou…ôh, pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   